<tr id="L161"><td><a href="#L161">161</a></td><td>LASARAN [on monitor]:  You haven't been listening. I don't have time. Once I leave here, I can't contact you again. I have to know if you're going to be there or not, and I have to know now.</td></tr>

<tr id="L162"><td><a href="#L162">162</a></td><td>WORF:  We will be there.</td></tr>

